title: august 18: the day the lights went out in Indonesia
description:
In this episode of 365 days with mxmtoon, Maia talks about a day in 2005 when over 100 million people in Indonesia lost power. After, Maia discusses the polarizing musician Kid Rock. Listen to this episode today and make sure you’re following along with the daily updates @365daysmxmtoon on all platforms.
